                                <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"></path></svg>
                            </span>
                        </summary>
                        <div class="px-8 pb-6 text-slate-600 leading-relaxed border-t border-slate-50 pt-4">
                            <p>Experience hands-on learning in our state-of-the-art laboratories and innovation centers designed to mimic real-world industry environments.</p>
                        </div>
                    </details>

                    <details class="group border-b border-slate-100">
                        <summary class="w-full px-8 py-6 text-left flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors list-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
